commit.message:
rs6000.c (rs6000_override_options): Don't se MASK_PPC_GFXOPT for 8540 or 8548.

	* config/rs6000/rs6000.c (rs6000_override_options): Don't se
	MASK_PPC_GFXOPT for 8540 or 8548.
